Interface ProductContainer

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ProductGroup, StorageUnit

    public interface ProductContainer
    Author:
    Capchu An interface for StorageUnits and ProductGroups. These objects can “contain” Products and Items, and are referred to generically as “product containers”.
